Description: DeskPilot AI-powered input method engine for fcitx5
 swift-ime is the input method engine of DeskPilot, an AI-powered
 personal assistant. It provides:
 .
  * Snippet expansion: type /trigger and get expanded text
  * Mixed Chinese-English input (pinyin + English, no switching needed)
  * Voice input via #asr trigger (requires audio-aura daemon)
  * Action triggers via #exec_* (requires geek-familiar)
 .
 This package contains the fcitx5 addon (.so) and its Rust runtime
 library.
